name: petStar.00060 - petStarJetPac
description:
petStar Interactive presents : petStarJetPac

Thank you for beta testing this experimental new hardware module for your chippy. It's important we collect data on the effectiveness of the petStarJetPac before releasing it to the public. See how many dots you can grab + report back once you get the hang of it.

-how-
R to restart
click + hold in desired direction to blast there
blasting costs fuel
don't run out
dots  = more fuel

PLZ NOTE this is meant to be played in the window. Full screen is not tested and has caused issues before but hey you do you.
